    <img src="/images/sad-dog-404.png" alt="Sad dog - page not found" style="max-width:220px;width:100%;margin-bottom:2rem;" />
    <h1 style="font-size:2.5em; margin-bottom:0.5em;">404 ‚Äì Page Not Found</h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.2em; color:var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom:2em;">Sorry, we couldn‚Äôt find that page.<br />Try the menu or return to the <a href="/">homepage</a>.</p>
    <a href="/" class="button primary">Back to Home</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
